snippet: The couple met at Duke, from which they both graduated.
lead_paragraph: Shelby Rose Prichard, the daughter of Tami and Pat Prichard of Ransom Canyon, Tex., was married Saturday to Douglas Walker Barrows, a son of Judith J. Barrows and Dr. Albert A. Barrows III of Yarmouth Port, Mass. The Rev. Bonnie M. Connor, a Unity minister, officiated at the Winfield Inn, an events space in Kyle, Tex. The couple met at Duke, from which they both graduated, she cum laude.
